0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18977,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/al-ayn-haqq-ghusl\/","url_meta":{"origin":18986,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ayn: Beware evil eye of envy, perform ghusl","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe evil eye is real. If anything could precede the divine decree, it would be preceded by the evil eye. When you are asked to perform a ritual bath, then do so.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2188 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18981,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/prophet-refuge-hasan-husayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":18986,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge for Hasan and Husayn","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek refuge for his grandsons Hasan and Husayn, saying, \u201cVerily, your forefather would seek refuge for Ishmael and Isaac. I seek refuge in the perfect words of Allah from every devil and scourge and every harmful eye.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31961,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/11\/seek-refuge-in-allah-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":18986,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge from travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Sarjis reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say when he traveled, \u201cO Allah, You are the companion on the journey and the caretaker of the family. O Allah, accompany us on our journey and take care of our families. I seek refuge in You\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/24\/ibn-sirin-on-hasad\/","url_meta":{"origin":18986,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Sirin on Hasad: How could I envy anyone in the world?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Yunus ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: Ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI have never envied anyone over something they had in the world. For if he was among the people of Paradise, how could I envy him for something in the world while he will be sent to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18986","targetHints":{"allow":["GET